  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare 2nd line XELIRI/FOLFIRI + simvastatin vs
      XELIRI/FOLFIRI + placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To compare progression free survival of the standard second line chemotherapy (FOLFIRI,
      XELIRI) plus simvastatin in metastatic colorectal cancer patients. This trial is a
      placebo-controlled study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
